rows.label: tlk006401_07_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey. Ririo and his gang are really
coming along - they can go salvaging
without supervision now and all!

rows.label: tlk006401_07_msg0002
rows.name:
We'd never have discovered raw
talent like theirs if you hadn't got us
to hire them.

rows.label: tlk006401_07_msg0003
rows.name: You've got a real eye for people, Rex.

rows.label: tlk006401_07_msg0004
rows.name:
In any case, we've got us a promising
bunch of up-and-coming salvagers for
your trouble, and for that, I'm grateful.
